<section class="services">
  <article>
    <div class="services__intro">
      <p>
        At Westtown Websites, we deliver more than just websites—we build online
        experiences that help your business grow. Specializing in custom,
        performance-driven, and SEO-friendly web design, we craft solutions that
        not only showcase your brand but also improve your search engine
        visibility and user experience.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
<section class="services services--grid">
  <article>
    <div class="services__intro">
      <h3 class="services__heading">What We Offer</h3>
      <p class="services__subheading">
        Tailored Web Design and Development Solutions for Small Businesses
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <div id="services-list" class="services__grid" role="list">
    <div class="services__item" role="listitem">
      <h3 class="services__item-title">Tailored Web Design for Your Brand</h3>
      <p class="services__item-description">
        We don’t do cookie-cutter designs. Our websites are crafted specifically
        for your business, reflecting your brand’s unique personality while
        being fully responsive. Whether on desktop or mobile, your site will
        look stunning and professional.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services__item" role="listitem">
      <h3 class="services__item-title">Fast, Clean, and Efficient Code</h3>
      <p class="services__item-description">
        Our front-end development focuses on delivering a seamless user
        experience with performance in mind. Every line of code is hand-written
        to ensure your website loads quickly, runs smoothly, and performs
        optimally—giving your visitors an experience that keeps them coming
        back.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services__item" role="listitem">
      <h3 class="services__item-title">
        Make Your Website Accessible to Everyone
      </h3>
      <p class="services__item-description">
        We build websites that are accessible to all users, meeting the latest
        ADA compliance standards. From optimized navigation to screen-reader
        compatibility, we ensure that everyone, regardless of ability, can
        interact with your site with ease.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services__item" role="listitem">
      <h3 class="services__item-title">Engaging, Branded Email Templates</h3>
      <p class="services__item-description">
        Boost your email marketing with custom-designed, responsive templates.
        We create emails that align with your brand and perform flawlessly
        across devices, increasing your open and click-through rates.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services__item" role="listitem">
      <h3 class="services__item-title">
        Comprehensive SEO & Accessibility Audits
      </h3>
      <p class="services__item-description">
        Ensure your site is optimized for search engines and accessible to all.
        We perform in-depth audits, pinpointing areas for improvement in SEO
        rankings, load times, and ADA compliance to help you stay competitive.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services__item" role="listitem">
      <h3 class="services__item-title">
        AI Chatbots for Better Customer Engagement
      </h3>
      <p class="services__item-description">
        Offer your customers instant support with AI-powered chatbots. We
        integrate intelligent chat solutions that can answer queries, streamline
        sales, and improve overall customer experience, available 24/7.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services__item" role="listitem">
      <h3 class="services__item-title">Custom E-commerce Integration</h3>
      <p class="services__item-description">
        Ready to sell online? We design and build e-commerce platforms tailored
        to your products, ensuring a smooth and secure shopping experience for
        your customers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services__item" role="listitem">
      <h3 class="services__item-title">Speed Up and Optimize Your Website</h3>
      <p class="services__item-description">
        Website speed is crucial for retaining visitors. We optimize your site's
        performance to ensure fast load times, reduced bounce rates, and
        improved user engagement.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

